---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import Expertise from "../components/Expertise.astro";
import CasesPreview from "../components/CasesPreview.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Twinpixel | Webdesign Wageningen"
  description="Premium webdesign en development vanuit Wageningen. Design, performance en SEO in één lijn."
>
  <Hero />
    <section class="section value" aria-label="Waarom Twinpixel">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="value-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="kicker">USP</p>
          <h2 class="h2">Performance-first met directe lijnen</h2>
          <p class="lead small">
            We werken zonder tussenschijven. Je spreekt direct met de makers die design, build,
            performance en SEO aanpakken. Geen rommel, wel meetbare resultaten.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillars">
          <div class="pill">
            <p class="pill-title">Snel en strak</p>
            <p class="pill-text">Astro builds, geoptimaliseerde assets en Core Web Vitals-checks.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pill">
            <p class="pill-title">Heldere structuur</p>
            <p class="pill-text">Contentflows en CTA’s die logisch lezen en converteren.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pill">
            <p class="pill-title">Onderhoudbaar</p>
            <p class="pill-text">Component-gedreven UI, klaar voor iteratie en schaal.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pill">
            <p class="pill-title">Samenwerken</p>
            <p class="pill-text">Korte feedbackloops, vaste contactpersoon en duidelijke planning.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Expertise />
  <CasesPreview />

  <!-- Reviews Section -->
  <section class="section reviews" aria-label="Klant reviews">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reviews-header">
        <p class="kicker">Reviews</p>
        <h2 class="h2">Wat klanten zeggen</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Directe feedback van ondernemers die we hebben geholpen met hun online aanwezigheid.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reviews-carousel">
        <div class="reviews-track">
          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="review-text">
              "Professioneel team dat precies begrijpt wat je nodig hebt. De website laadt razendsnel
              en ziet er strak uit. Direct contact zonder tussenpersonen maakt het werken heel prettig."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-name">Sarah van der Berg</div>
              <div class="author-company">Eigenaar, Studio Creatief</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="review-text">
              "Van idee tot live website in korte tijd. Uitstekende communicatie en het eindresultaat
              overtrof mijn verwachtingen. Zeker aan te raden voor ondernemers die serieus zijn over hun online presence."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-name">Mark de Vries</div>
              <div class="author-company">Directeur, TechSolutions B.V.</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="review-text">
              "De technische kennis is duidelijk aanwezig. Ze denken mee over SEO en performance,
              niet alleen over het design. Een website die echt werkt voor mijn bedrijf."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-name">Lisa Jansen</div>
              <div class="author-company">Marketing Manager, GreenTech</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="review-text">
              "Snelle oplevering, transparante prijzen en een website die perfect aansluit bij mijn huisstijl.
              Het contact was persoonlijk en professioneel. Top werk!"
            </blockquote>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-name">Tom Bakker</div>
              <div class="author-company">Eigenaar, Bakker & Zn</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="review-text">
              "Ze luisteren echt naar je wensen en komen met slimme oplossingen. De website is niet alleen mooi,
              maar ook nog eens supersnel. Een investering die zichzelf terugverdient."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-name">Anna Smit</div>
              <div class="author-company">Founder, Anna's Coaching</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
              <span class="star">★</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="review-text">
              "Professioneel van begin tot eind. Duidelijke afspraken, snelle communicatie en een eindresultaat
              waar ik trots op ben. Zeker voor herhaling vatbaar!"
            </blockquote>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="author-name">Robert van Dijk</div>
              <div class="author-company">CEO, InnovateIT</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reviews-cta">
        <p class="reviews-note">
          Deze reviews zijn afkomstig van onze Google Business Profile.
          <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Twinpixel/@51.980899,5.6787299,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0xa7b2749962b349e7:0x556d7170e66ed503!8m2!3d51.980899!4d5.6813048!9m1!1b1!16s%2Fg%2F11x0p6wbdm?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI1MTIwOS4wIKXMDSoKLDEwMDc5MjA2OUgBUAM%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Bekijk alle reviews →
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section packages" aria-label="Pakketten">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="head">
        <p class="kicker">Pakketten</p>
        <h2 class="h2">Kies wat past bij je vraag</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="pkg-grid">
        <div class="pkg">
          <p class="pkg-name">Branding Sprint</p>
          <p class="pkg-price">Vanaf €2.500</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Merkbasics: logo, kleuren, typografie</li>
            <li>Mini styleguide + component starters</li>
            <li>Templates voor social/presentaties</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pkg">
          <p class="pkg-name">Website Launch</p>
          <p class="pkg-price">Vanaf €3.500</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Homepage + diensten + contactflow</li>
            <li>SEO-basics en performance checks</li>
            <li>Lead-captures en analytics setup</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pkg">
          <p class="pkg-name">Technical Build</p>
          <p class="pkg-price">Vanaf €5.500</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Integraties (CRM, forms, analytics)</li>
            <li>Custom flows/filters/dashboards</li>
            <li>Component-architectuur + QA</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section faq" aria-label="Veelgestelde vragen">
    <div class="container faq-wrap">
      <div class="faq-head">
        <p class="kicker">FAQ</p>
        <h2 class="h2">Veelgestelde vragen</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-accordion">
        <details>
          <summary>
            <span>Wat hebben jullie van mij nodig?</span>
            <span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p>Doel, doelgroep, gewenste pagina’s en voorbeelden van wat je goed vindt. Content in concept helpt, anders schrijven we mee aan structuur/microcopy.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>
            <span>Hoe snel kunnen jullie opleveren?</span>
            <span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p>Een standaard site in 3–5 weken, afhankelijk van feedback en content. Technische projecten plannen we samen in fases.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>
            <span>Regelen jullie hosting en onderhoud?</span>
            <span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p>Ja, we kunnen deployen op Netlify/Vercel en helpen met monitoring/updates. Of we leveren op zodat je eigen team het beheert.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>
            <span>Kunnen jullie SEO meenemen?</span>
            <span class="chev" aria-hidden="true">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p>Ja: technische SEO, titles/headings, interne links en performance. Voor content/long-form werken we samen met copywriters.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-cta" id="contact" aria-label="Contact call to action">
    <div class="cta">
      <div class="content">
        <p class="kicker">Contact</p>
        <h2 class="title">Een idee bespreken?</h2>
        <p class="text">
          Vertel kort wat je wilt maken, waarom het belangrijk is en wanneer je het nodig hebt.
          We reageren snel met een voorstel, planning en wat we meenemen op het gebied van design,
          performance en SEO.
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
          <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" label="Plan Kennismaking" />
          <a
            class="btn secondary"
            href="mailto:meurstwan@gmail.com?subject=Contact%20via%20website"
          >
            Mail Direct
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
      .contact-cta {
        margin: 3.6rem 0 0;
      }

      .cta {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2.2rem 2.4rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      }

      .content {
        max-width: 640px;
      }

      .kicker {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        opacity: 0.72;
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      }

      .title {
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
        font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 2.6vw, 2.15rem);
        line-height: 1.15;
      }

      .text {
        margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
        opacity: 0.88;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 54ch;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 0.78rem 1.1rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      }

      .btn.primary {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        color: #0b1321;
      }

      .btn.primary:hover {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
      }

      .btn.secondary {
        background: transparent;
        opacity: 0.88;
      }

      .btn.secondary:hover {
        opacity: 1;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .cta {
          padding: 1.8rem 1.6rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </section>

  <style>
    .section{
      padding: 70px 0;
    }
    .container{
      width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 2rem));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .kicker{
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .h2{
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.15;
    }
    .lead.small{
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      max-width: 70ch;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.74);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .value-grid{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr .95fr;
      gap: 48px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .pillars{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .pill{
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.025);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 20px 20px 24px;
      transition: all .3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .pill::before{
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(47,137,255,.1), transparent);
      transition: left .5s ease;
    }
    .pill-title{
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-weight: 650;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
      transition: color .3s ease;
    }
    .pill-text{
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.70);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: color .3s ease;
    }
    .pill:hover{
      border-color: rgba(47,137,255,.4);
      background: rgba(47,137,255,.05);
      transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(47,137,255,.15);
    }
    .pill:hover::before{
      left: 100%;
    }
    .pill:hover .pill-title{
      color: rgba(47,137,255,.95);
    }
    .pill:hover .pill-text{
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.85);
    }

    .packages .head{
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .pkg-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .pkg{
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.025);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      display:grid;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: transform .16s ease, border-color .16s ease, box-shadow .16s ease, background-color .16s ease;
    }
    .pkg-name{ margin:0; font-weight: 650; font-size: 16px; }
    .pkg-price{ margin:0; color: rgba(255,255,255,.78); }
    .pkg ul{
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .pkg:hover{
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.22);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.16);
    }

    .faq-wrap{ display:grid; gap: 16px; }
    .faq-accordion{
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.025);
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
    }
    .faq-accordion details{
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      padding: 2px 0;
      transition: background-color .14s ease;
    }
    .faq-accordion details:last-of-type{
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .faq-accordion summary{
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      display:flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 16px 16px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
      font-weight: 650;
      transition: background-color .14s ease, color .14s ease;
    }
    .faq-accordion summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
    .faq-accordion summary .chev{ 
      opacity: .6; 
      transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1); 
      transition: transform .3s cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55), opacity .2s ease; 
    }
    .faq-accordion details[open] summary .chev{ 
      transform: rotate(180deg) scale(1.1); 
      opacity: 1;
    }
    .faq-accordion summary:hover{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.96);
    }
    .faq-accordion details[open]{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.03);
    }
    .faq-accordion p{
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0 16px 16px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .contact-cta .kicker{ margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }

    .footer{
      padding: 26px 0 40px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px){
      .value-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .pillars{ grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .pkg-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .faq-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 620px){
      .pillars{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    /* Reviews Section */
    .reviews {
      padding: 5rem 0;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01);
    }

    .reviews-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .reviews-header .kicker {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .reviews-header .h2 {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .reviews-header .lead {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .reviews-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .reviews-carousel {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .reviews-track {
      display: flex;
      width: calc(200px * 6); /* 6 reviews */
      animation: scrollReviews 45s linear infinite;
    }

    .reviews-track:hover {
      animation-play-state: paused;
    }

    .reviews-track .review-card {
      flex: 0 0 100vw;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 2rem;
      opacity: 0.7;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .reviews-track .review-card:nth-child(1) {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    @keyframes scrollReviews {
      0% { transform: translateX(0); }
      16.67% { transform: translateX(-100vw); }
      33.33% { transform: translateX(-200vw); }
      50% { transform: translateX(-300vw); }
      66.67% { transform: translateX(-400vw); }
      83.33% { transform: translateX(-500vw); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-600vw); }
    }

    .review-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
    }

    .review-card:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .review-stars {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .star {
      color: #fbbf24;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .review-text {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
      font-style: italic;
      position: relative;
    }

    .review-text::before {
      content: '"';
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: rgba(47,137,255,0.3);
      position: absolute;
      top: -0.5rem;
      left: -1rem;
      font-family: serif;
    }

    .review-author {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .author-name {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .author-company {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    }

    .reviews-cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .reviews-note {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .reviews-note a {
      color: #2F89FF;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .reviews-note a:hover {
      color: rgba(47,137,255,0.8);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .reviews {
        padding: 3rem 0;
      }

      .reviews-header .h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .reviews-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .reviews-carousel {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .reviews-track .review-card {
        flex: 0 0 85vw;
        margin: 0 1rem;
      }

      .review-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .reviews {
        padding: 2rem 0;
      }

      .reviews-header {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .reviews-header .h2 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }

      .reviews-header .lead {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .reviews-grid {
        gap: 1rem;
      }

